  provinceImage3: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 8434609c7b2e6ef48a384c76a3be14a4, type: 3}
  description: "Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh ven bi\u1EC3n thu\u1ED9c
    v\xF9ng Duy\xEAn h\u1EA3i Nam Trung B\u1ED9 c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam. Sau khi s\u1EAFp
    x\u1EBFp \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh, Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i v\u1EABn
    gi\u1EEF vai tr\xF2 l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh quan tr\u1ECDng c\u1EE7a khu v\u1EF1c
    mi\u1EC1n Trung v\u1EDBi \u0111\u1ECBa h\xECnh g\u1ED3m \u0111\u1ED3ng b\u1EB1ng
    ven bi\u1EC3n, v\xF9ng n\xFAi ph\xEDa t\xE2y v\xE0 c\xE1c \u0111\u1EA3o ngo\xE0i
    kh\u01A1i. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1 Qu\u1EA3ng
    Ng\xE3i. Nh\u1EEFng \u0111\u1ECBa danh n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh g\u1ED3m
    \u0110\u1EA3o L\xFD S\u01A1n, B\xE3i bi\u1EC3n M\u1EF9 Kh\xEA (Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i)
    v\xE0 Khu ch\u1EE9ng t\xEDch S\u01A1n M\u1EF9.\n\nQu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i n\u1ED5i
    ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1EB7c s\u1EA3n \u0111\u1ECBa ph\u01B0\u01A1ng
    nh\u01B0 T\u1ECFi L\xFD S\u01A1n, Don Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i v\xE0 C\xE1 b\u1ED1ng
    s\xF4ng Tr\xE0.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a, Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i mang \u0111\u1EADm
    b\u1EA3n s\u1EAFc v\u0103n h\xF3a c\u1EE7a c\u01B0 d\xE2n mi\u1EC1n Trung ven
    bi\u1EC3n. T\u1EC9nh c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u l\u1EC5 h\u1ED9i truy\u1EC1n th\u1ED1ng
    g\u1EAFn v\u1EDBi \u0111\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng ng\u01B0 d\xE2n, ti\xEAu bi\u1EC3u
    nh\u01B0 L\u1EC5 khao l\u1EC1 th\u1EBF l\xEDnh Ho\xE0ng Sa, nh\u1EB1m t\u01B0\u1EDFng
    nh\u1EDB nh\u1EEFng \u0111\u1ED9i h\xF9ng binh Ho\xE0ng Sa t\u1EEBng ra bi\u1EC3n
    b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 ch\u1EE7 quy\u1EC1n c\u1EE7a \u0111\u1EA5t n\u01B0\u1EDBc."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 01/7/2025, t\u1EC9nh Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i v\xE0 t\u1EC9nh
    Kon Tum ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c s\xE1p nh\u1EADp, h\xECnh th\xE0nh \u0111\u01A1n v\u1ECB
    h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh m\u1EDBi l\u1EA5y t\xEAn l\xE0 t\u1EC9nh Qu\u1EA3ng Ng\xE3i.
    T\u1EC9nh m\u1EDBi c\xF3 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch t\u1EF1 nhi\xEAn 14.832,548km vu\xF4ng\r                                   
    v\xE0 quy m\xF4 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 tr\xEAn 2,1 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, h\u01B0\u1EDBng
    t\u1EDBi m\u1EDF r\u1ED9ng kh\xF4ng gian ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n, k\u1EBFt h\u1EE3p
    l\u1EE3i th\u1EBF ven bi\u1EC3n v\xE0 T\xE2y Nguy\xEAn."
